				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h3>Extended Engagement – <br />Recruitment Process Outsourcing</h3>
<p>Let us become your recruiting department for a specific period that you define. This option is ideal if you know you will have talent acquisition needs for a specified term, for example three or six months.  Maybe your company is planning for a growth spurt over the next six months, and you anticipate ongoing needs for adding talent and experience. We can help.</p>
<p><strong>We offer a turn-key service, providing:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>On-going Talent Search</li>
<li>Full Service Job Posting and Recruitment assistance</li>
<li>Screening and Assessment of candidates</li>
<li>Billed Monthly</li>
</ul></div>
