				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h3>On-Demand Recruiting Services <br />(build your own solution)</h3>
<p>If your needs for new talent are less predictable or on a smaller scale, maybe the one-step-at-a-time approach would better match your needs. We offer a number of on-demand recruiting services, allowing you to engage us just for what you need, when you need it.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>On-demand Placement</li>
<li>Recruiting Strategy Consulting</li>
<li>Recruiting Program Audit &amp; Evaluation</li>
<li>Career Coaching &amp; Outplacement</li>
<li>Performance Modeling &amp; Assessment</li>
<li>Employer Brand Audits</li>
</ul></div>
